{"tid":1612709,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"星島追緊大公成為Fake News之首!!","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:59:03.000Z","uid":88664,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7139c6f9a47a8302e0ebc106e13fb1201cfddce","tid":1612709,"uid":88664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"吳文遠 Avery Ng<br />\n7 小時 &middot; <br />\n呢個訪問感覺好古怪，所以我即時打電話問古思堯，佢話係琴日遊行完，有個星島記者約佢去間茶樓做訪問。訪問期間，古思堯強調佢唔係社民連成員，只係保釣行動委員會成員，訪問亦都只係用個人身份。<br />\n最令我覺得奇怪嘅係，呢段報道寫：（古思堯）總結道，「社民連不贊成獨立，堅決反對暴力，反對推動香港獨立。」<br />\n我問古思堯有冇講過呢句，古思堯話佢冇咁樣講過。<br />\n成件事好奇怪，成個故仔frame做一個社民連成員嘅專訪，而好明顯古思堯唔係社民連成員。希望大家唔好中計，呢個故仔明顯搞分化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1603159/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%8F%A4%E6%80%9D%E5%A0%AF-%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E7%84%A1%E8%B7%AF%E8%B5%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1603159%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B5%25B0&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=cdd8a8e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1603159%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B5%25B0&h=5bbb8d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1603159/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%8F%A4%E6%80%9D%E5%A0%AF-%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E7%84%A1%E8%B7%AF%E8%B5%B0</a>"},{"pid":"3713aa16bf6f92cb5563abfcacb14ce36d9584ec","tid":1612709,"uid":88664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠 Leung Yiu Chung<br />\n9月30日 15:11 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n9月30日《星島日報》有篇報導，標題為「梁耀忠：暴力抗爭不能解決問題」。當中內文第一段，載有「....梁耀忠表示，暴力抗爭不能解決問題，希望示威者冷靜下來。...」|<br />\n<br />\n謹此澄清，在採訪過程中，沒有表示過「暴力抗爭不能解決問題」以及「要示威者冷靜」。<br />\n<br />\n近期警方執法過程中，展現的暴行，令人齒冷；抗爭者甚至普通市民遭警員毆打和濫捕，實在使人感到非常痛心。在訪問中一直重申的重點是，政府必須要回應民間的五大訴求，否則是解決不了問題的。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，警方的濫用暴力，更加解決不了當前的社會問題，只會令問題愈益惡化。"},{"pid":"31867b87593af25e3e3e82ba26998124ae6474c0","tid":1612709,"uid":88664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"搞緊分化，等你地屌返你地o既人"},{"pid":"4a44df494e10ed39e151372c83b3160e8aa0b647","tid":1612709,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"好多中學派星島 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30da4e7e04d688c42e2d1a598c2206f6daa01ec1","tid":1612709,"uid":88664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31867b87593af25e3e3e82ba26998124ae6474c0","tid":1612709,"uid":88664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"搞緊分化，等你地屌返你地o既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"雖然梁耀忠都係膠架喇<br />\n同埋接受星島訪問都已經係on99! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43fb19507134165325b876b6ff12ff7fd1af06d","tid":1612709,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55717cb40d2799d5aff72774653c9cb265e6f44","tid":1612709,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"其實一向勁多fake new